<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - gẖyrt ḥyạty bḥb ʿjyb wmʿạk fy smạk bqy̱ ly nṣyb 1- ạkẖtrt tjyny wạnạ wsṭ ạnyny mdyt ly ạydyk ạlḥlwẗ wʿynyk tsbyny nsytny ạlạ̉my rjʿt slạmy wạdytny frḥẗ wbhjẗ ( wmsẖyt qdạmy )2 2- wbḍʿfy hạjylk yạ yswʿ wạnạdylk tgẖslny bqwẗ dmk yrfʿny ṣlybk tsẖfy ly jrwḥy wtbdl nwḥy bsʿạdẗ wnṣrẗ fy sẖkẖṣk ( tnʿsẖ ly rwḥy )2 3- ạ̉yạmy ạljạyẗ fy ạydyk mḥmyẗ msẖ kẖạyf ʿạlmstqbl ʿsẖạn ạnt rạʿy̱ wạtẖq fy wʿwdk mlạzmny wjwdk wḥyạty ạnt gẖạmrhạ ( bạlkẖyr mn jwdk )2</lyrics>
